%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'themeVariables': {'fontSize': '14px'}}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start([User launches forge-chat.py]) --> Input[/User describes a task\n'Build me an agent that reviews PRs'/]

    Input --> Parse[Agent Forge parses the request\nExtracts: purpose, domain,\ncapabilities, risk level]

    Parse --> Search{Search for\nexisting agents}

    Search --> |gh search repos| GitHub[(GitHub API)]
    GitHub --> Results{Matching\nagents found?}

    Results --> |Yes| Evaluate[Evaluate fitness\n- Skills match?\n- Actively maintained?\n- Extensible?]
    Evaluate --> Recommend{Strong match?}

    Recommend --> |Yes - exact match| Reuse[Recommend reusing\nexisting agent]
    Reuse --> ShowReuse[/Display agent details:\nname, skills, URL, how to run/]
    ShowReuse --> Done

    Recommend --> |Partial match| Fork[Recommend forking\nand extending]
    Fork --> Confirm1{User approves?}
    Confirm1 --> |Yes| ForkRepo[Fork repo + add new skills]
    Confirm1 --> |No| Scaffold

    Recommend --> |No match| Scaffold

    Results --> |No| Scaffold[Scaffold new gitagent]

    Scaffold --> Design[Design agent architecture\n- agent.yaml manifest\n- SOUL.md identity\n- RULES.md boundaries\n- Skills and tools]

    Design --> Preview[/Show user the proposed:\nagent.yaml + SOUL.md\nskills list + tool list/]

    Preview --> Confirm2{User approves\nthe design?}
    Confirm2 --> |No - feedback| Revise[Revise based on\nuser feedback]
    Revise --> Design

    Confirm2 --> |Yes| Create[Create GitHub repository\ngh repo create]
    Create --> Push[Add all gitagent files\nCommit + push to GitHub]
    Push --> Validate[Run gitagent validate\nConfirm spec compliance]

    Validate --> |Pass| Report[/Report to user:\n- Agent name + version\n- GitHub repo URL\n- Skills and tools list\n- Export commands/]
    Validate --> |Fail| Fix[Fix validation errors]
    Fix --> Validate

    Report --> Done([User has a deployable agent])

    Done --> Export{User wants to\nexport?}
    Export --> |Claude Code| CC[gitagent export -f claude-code]
    Export --> |OpenClaw| OC[gitagent export -f openclaw]
    Export --> |OpenAI| OA[gitagent export -f openai]
    Export --> |CrewAI| CR[gitagent export -f crewai]
    Export --> |System prompt| SP[gitagent export -f system-prompt]

